Package it.polimi.ingsw.view.client.gui

Class GUInterface

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.view.client.ClientView
it.polimi.ingsw.view.client.gui.GUInterface
All Implemented Interfaces:
ClientUpdateViewInterface, GUIViewInterface, InputViewInterface, UpdateViewInterface
public class GUInterface extends ClientView implements GUIViewInterface
Class representing the GUI. It receives messages from the server and updates the controllers. It sends the client's input to the server.
